<p><span class="vocab">挨拶<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>挨拶</rb><rt>あいさつ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;greetings; introductions</span></span>をしたうちに<span class="vocab">教頭<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>教頭</rb><rt>きょうとう</rt></ruby>&nbsp;head teacher</span></span>の<span class="vocab">なにがし<span class="vocabdef">なにがし&nbsp;of a certain name</span></span>と<span class="vocab">云う<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>云</rb><rt>い</rt></ruby>う&nbsp;called</span></span>のが<span class="vocab">居た<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>居</rb><rt>い</rt></ruby>た&nbsp;there was</span></span>。これは<span class="vocab">文学士<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>文学士</rb><rt>ぶんがくし</rt></ruby>&nbsp;degree holder</span></span>だそうだ。文学士と云えば<span class="vocab">大学<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>大学</rb><rt>だいがく</rt></ruby>&nbsp;university</span></span>の<span class="vocab">卒業生<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>卒業生</rb><rt>そつぎょうせい</rt></ruby>&nbsp;graduate</span></span>だからえらい<span class="vocab">人<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>人</rb><rt>ひと</rt></ruby>&nbsp;person</span></span>なんだろう。<span class="vocab">妙に<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>妙</rb><rt>みょう</rt></ruby>に&nbsp;strangely</span></span><span class="vocab">女のような<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>女</rb><rt>おんな</rt></ruby>のような&nbsp;effeminate; woman-like</span></span><span class="vocab">優しい<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>優</rb><rt>やさ</rt></ruby>しい&nbsp;gentle; delicate; soft</span></span><span class="vocab">声<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>声</rb><rt>こえ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;voice</span></span>を<span class="vocab">出す<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>出</rb><rt>だ</rt></ruby>す&nbsp;speak (voice)</span></span>人だった。もっとも<span class="vocab">驚いた<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>驚</rb><rt>おどろ</rt></ruby>いた&nbsp;surprising</span></span>のはこの<span class="vocab">暑い<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>暑</rb><rt>あつ</rt></ruby>い&nbsp;hot (weather)</span></span>のにフランネルの<span class="vocab">襯衣<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>襯衣</rb><rt>しゃつ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;shirt</span></span>を<span class="vocab">着ている<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>着</rb><rt>き</rt></ruby>ている&nbsp;was wearing</span></span>。いくらか<span class="vocab">薄い<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>薄</rb><rt>うす</rt></ruby>い&nbsp;thin; light</span></span><span class="vocab">地<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>地</rb><rt>じ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;fabric</span></span>には<span class="vocab">相違なくっても<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>相違</rb><rt>そうい</rt></ruby>なくっても&nbsp;even though there's no doubt that</span></span>暑いには<span class="vocab">極ってる<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>極</rb><rt>きま</rt></ruby>っている&nbsp;is certain; is a given</span></span>。文学士だけに<span class="vocab">ご苦労千万<span class="vocabdef">ご<ruby><rb>苦労千万</rb><rt>くろうせんばん</rt></ruby>&nbsp;extreme effort; great pains</span></span>な<span class="vocab">服装<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>服装</rb><rt>なり</rt></ruby>&nbsp;appearance; dress</span></span>をしたもんだ。しかもそれが<span class="vocab">赤シャツ<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>赤</rb><rt>あか</rt></ruby>シャツ&nbsp;red shirt</span></span>だから人を<span class="vocab">馬鹿<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>馬鹿</rb><rt>ばか</rt></ruby>&nbsp;fool; idiot</span></span>にしている。あとから<span class="vocab">聞いたら<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>聞</rb><rt>き</rt></ruby>いたら&nbsp;asked; inquired</span></span>この<span class="vocab">男<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>男</rb><rt>おとこ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;man</span></span>は<span class="vocab">年が年中<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>年</rb><rt>ねん</rt></ruby>が<ruby><rb>年中</rb><rt>ねんじゅう</rt></ruby>&nbsp;year round</span></span>赤シャツを着るんだそうだ。妙な<span class="vocab">病気<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>病気</rb><rt>びょうき</rt></ruby>&nbsp;illness; affliction</span></span>があった<span class="vocab">者<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>者</rb><rt>もの</rt></ruby>&nbsp;person; individual</span></span>だ。<span class="vocab">当人<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>当人</rb><rt>とうにん</rt></ruby>&nbsp;the person in question</span></span>の<span class="vocab">説明<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>説明</rb><rt>せつめい</rt></ruby>&nbsp;explanation; story</span></span>では赤は<span class="vocab">身体<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>身体</rb><rt>からだ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;body; physical condition</span></span>に<span class="vocab">薬<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>薬</rb><rt>くすり</rt></ruby>&nbsp;medicine</span></span>になるから、<span class="vocab">衛生<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>衛生</rb><rt>えいせい</rt></ruby>&nbsp;health</span></span>のために<span class="vocab">わざわざ<span class="vocabdef">わざわざ&nbsp;specially; expressly</span></span><span class="vocab">誂らえる<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>誂</rb><rt>あつ</rt></ruby>らえる&nbsp;place a custom order</span></span>んだそうだが、<span class="vocab">入らざる<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>入</rb><rt>い</rt></ruby>らざる&nbsp;unnecessary</span></span><span class="vocab">心配<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>心配</rb><rt>しんぱい</rt></ruby>&nbsp;concern</span></span>だ。そんならついでに<span class="vocab">着物<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>着物</rb><rt>きもの</rt></ruby>&nbsp;kimono (coat)</span></span>も<span class="vocab">袴<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>袴</rb><rt>はかま</rt></ruby>&nbsp;(formal Japanese) pants</span></span>も赤にすればいい。それから<span class="vocab">英語<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>英語</rb><rt>えいご</rt></ruby>&nbsp;English</span></span>の<span class="vocab">教師<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>教師</rb><rt>きょうし</rt></ruby>&nbsp;instructor</span></span>に<span class="vocab">古賀<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>古賀</rb><rt>こが</rt></ruby>&nbsp;Koga (name)</span></span>とか云う<span class="vocab">大変<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>大変</rb><rt>たいへん</rt></ruby>&nbsp;terribly</span></span><span class="vocab">顔色<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>顔色</rb><rt>かおいろ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;complexion; facial color</span></span>の<span class="vocab">悪るい<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>悪</rb><rt>わ</rt></ruby>るい&nbsp;bad; unwell</span></span>男が居た。<span class="vocab">大概<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>大概</rb><rt>たいがい</rt></ruby>&nbsp;in general</span></span><span class="vocab">顔<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>顔</rb><rt>かお</rt></ruby>&nbsp;face</span></span>の<span class="vocab">蒼い<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>蒼</rb><rt>あお</rt></ruby>い&nbsp;pale; sickly (lit: blue)</span></span>人は<span class="vocab">瘠せてる<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>瘠</rb><rt>や</rt></ruby>せてる&nbsp;thin; lean; gaunt</span></span>もんだがこの男は蒼く<span class="vocab">ふくれている<span class="vocabdef">ふくれている&nbsp;swollen</span></span>。<span class="vocab">昔<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>昔</rb><rt>むかし</rt></ruby>&nbsp;long ago</span></span><span class="vocab">小学校<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>小学校</rb><rt>しょうがっこう</rt></ruby>&nbsp;elementary school</span></span>へ<span class="vocab">行く<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>行</rb><rt>い</rt></ruby>く&nbsp;go (to school)</span></span><span class="vocab">時分<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>時分</rb><rt>じぶん</rt></ruby>&nbsp;time; period</span></span>、<span class="vocab">浅井の民さん<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>浅井</rb><rt>あさい</rt></ruby>の<ruby><rb>民</rb><rt>たみ</rt></ruby>さん&nbsp;Tami (first name) Asai (family name)</span></span>と云う<span class="vocab">子<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>子</rb><rt>こ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;child</span></span>が<span class="vocab">同級生<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>同級生</rb><rt>どうきゅうせい</rt></ruby>&nbsp;classmate</span></span>にあったが、この浅井の<span class="vocab">おやじ<span class="vocabdef">おやじ&nbsp;father</span></span>がやはり、こんな<span class="vocab">色つや<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>色</rb><rt>いろ</rt></ruby>つや&nbsp;complexion; color</span></span>だった。<span class="vocab">浅井<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>浅井</rb><rt>あさい</rt></ruby>&nbsp;Mr. Asai</span></span>は<span class="vocab">百姓<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>百姓</rb><rt>ひゃくしょう</rt></ruby>&nbsp;farmer</span></span>だから、百姓になるとあんな顔になるかと<span class="vocab">清<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>清</rb><rt>きよ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;Kiyo (name of Botchan's former maidservant)</span></span>に聞いてみたら、そうじゃありません、あの人は<span class="vocab">うらなり<span class="vocabdef">うらなり&nbsp;fruit grown near the top end of the vine</span></span>の<span class="vocab">唐茄子<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>唐茄子</rb><rt>とうなす</rt></ruby>&nbsp;pumpkin; squash</span></span>ばかり<span class="vocab">食べる<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>食</rb><rt>た</rt></ruby>べる&nbsp;eat</span></span>から、蒼くふくれるんですと<span class="vocab">教えて<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>教</rb><rt>おし</rt></ruby>えて&nbsp;explain; inform; teach</span></span>くれた。<span class="vocab">それ以来<span class="vocabdef">それ<ruby><rb>以来</rb><rt>いらい</rt></ruby>&nbsp;since that (time)</span></span>蒼くふくれた人を<span class="vocab">見れば<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>見</rb><rt>み</rt></ruby>れば&nbsp;(when I) see</span></span><span class="vocab">必ず<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>必</rb><rt>かなら</rt></ruby>ず&nbsp;invariably</span></span>うらなりの唐茄子を<span class="vocab">食った<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>食</rb><rt>く</rt></ruby>った&nbsp;ate</span></span><span class="vocab">酬い<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>酬</rb><rt>むく</rt></ruby>い&nbsp;payback (for); result of</span></span>だと<span class="vocab">思う<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>思</rb><rt>おも</rt></ruby>う&nbsp;think; consider</span></span>。この英語の教師もうらなりばかり食ってるに<span class="vocab">違いない<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>違</rb><rt>ちが</rt></ruby>いない&nbsp;no doubt</span></span>。もっともうらなりとは<span class="vocab">何の事<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>何</rb><rt>なん</rt></ruby>の<ruby><rb>事</rb><rt>こと</rt></ruby>&nbsp;what sort of thing</span></span>か<span class="vocab">今もって<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>今</rb><rt>いま</rt></ruby>もって&nbsp;still; even now</span></span>知らない。清に聞いてみた<span class="vocab">事<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>事</rb><rt>こと</rt></ruby>&nbsp;act; fact</span></span>はあるが、清は<span class="vocab">笑って<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>笑</rb><rt>わら</rt></ruby>って&nbsp;laughed</span></span><span class="vocab">答えなかった<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>答</rb><rt>こた</rt></ruby>えなかった&nbsp;didn't answer</span></span>。<span class="vocab">大方<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>大方</rb><rt>おおかた</rt></ruby>&nbsp;probably</span></span>清も知らないんだろう。それからおれと<span class="vocab">同じ<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>同</rb><rt>おな</rt></ruby>じ&nbsp;the same</span></span><span class="vocab">数学<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>数学</rb><rt>すうがく</rt></ruby>&nbsp;mathematics</span></span>の教師に<span class="vocab">堀田<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>堀田</rb><rt>ほった</rt></ruby>&nbsp;Hotta (name)</span></span>というのが居た。これは<span class="vocab">逞しい<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>逞</rb><rt>たくま</rt></ruby>しい&nbsp;stout; brawny</span></span><span class="vocab">毬栗<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>毬栗</rb><rt>いがぐり</rt></ruby>&nbsp;close-cropped head (lit: chestnut with burrs)</span></span><span class="vocab">坊主<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>坊主</rb><rt>ぼうず</rt></ruby>&nbsp;monk; one with a shaved head</span></span>で、<span class="vocab">叡山<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>叡山</rb><rt>えいざん</rt></ruby>&nbsp;Eizan (name of a temple)</span></span>の<span class="vocab">悪僧<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>悪僧</rb><rt>あくそう</rt></ruby>&nbsp;renegade monk</span></span>と云うべき<span class="vocab">面構<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>面構</rb><rt>つらがまえ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;look; facial expression</span></span>である。<span class="vocab">人<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>人</rb><rt>ひと</rt></ruby>&nbsp;a person (Botchan in this case)</span></span>が<span class="vocab">叮寧に<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>叮寧</rb><rt>ていねい</rt></ruby>に&nbsp;politely</span></span><span class="vocab">辞令<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>辞令</rb><rt>じれい</rt></ruby>&nbsp;letter of appointment</span></span>を<span class="vocab">見せたら<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>見</rb><rt>み</rt></ruby>せたら&nbsp;showed</span></span><span class="vocab">見向き<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>見向</rb><rt>みむ</rt></ruby>き&nbsp;looking toward; taking notice of</span></span>もせず、やあ<span class="vocab">君<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>君</rb><rt>きみ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;you</span></span>が<span class="vocab">新任<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>新任</rb><rt>しんにん</rt></ruby>&nbsp;new man; new hire</span></span>の人か、ちと<span class="vocab">遊び<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>遊</rb><rt>あそ</rt></ruby>び&nbsp;visit; social call</span></span>に<span class="vocab">来給え<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>来給</rb><rt>きたま</rt></ruby>え&nbsp;come over</span></span>アハハハと云った。<span class="vocab">何<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>何</rb><rt>なに</rt></ruby>&nbsp;what</span></span>がアハハハだ。そんな<span class="vocab">礼儀<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>礼儀</rb><rt>れいぎ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;manners; courtesy</span></span>を<span class="vocab">心得ぬ<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>心得</rb><rt>こころえ</rt></ruby>ぬ&nbsp;not be aware of</span></span><span class="vocab">奴<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>奴</rb><rt>やつ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;fellow</span></span>の<span class="vocab">所<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>所</rb><rt>ところ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;place; home</span></span>へ<span class="vocab">誰<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>誰</rb><rt>だれ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;who</span></span>が<span class="vocab">遊びに行く<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>遊</rb><rt>あそ</rt></ruby>びに<ruby><rb>行</rb><rt>い</rt></ruby>く&nbsp;pay a visit</span></span>ものか。おれはこの時からこの坊主に<span class="vocab">山嵐<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>山嵐</rb><rt>やまあらし</rt></ruby>&nbsp;Yama Arashi (mountain storm; frightful mountain deity)</span></span>という<span class="vocab">渾名<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>渾名</rb><rt>あだな</rt></ruby>&nbsp;nickname</span></span>をつけてやった。<span class="vocab">漢学<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>漢学</rb><rt>かんがく</rt></ruby>&nbsp;Chinese study; classics</span></span>の<span class="vocab">先生<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>先生</rb><rt>せんせい</rt></ruby>&nbsp;teacher</span></span>はさすがに<span class="vocab">堅い<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>堅</rb><rt>かた</rt></ruby>い&nbsp;stiff; formal</span></span>ものだ。<span class="vocab">昨日<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>昨日</rb><rt>さくじつ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;yesterday</span></span><span class="vocab">お着き<span class="vocabdef">お<ruby><rb>着</rb><rt>つ</rt></ruby>き&nbsp;arrival</span></span>で、さぞ<span class="vocab">お疲れ<span class="vocabdef">お<ruby><rb>疲</rb><rt>つか</rt></ruby>れ&nbsp;fatigue; exhaustion</span></span>で、それでもう<span class="vocab">授業<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>授業</rb><rt>じゅぎょう</rt></ruby>&nbsp;class</span></span>を<span class="vocab">お始め<span class="vocabdef">お<ruby><rb>始</rb><rt>はじ</rt></ruby>め&nbsp;begin</span></span>で、<span class="vocab">大分<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>大分</rb><rt>だいぶ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;considerable</span></span><span class="vocab">ご励精<span class="vocabdef">ご<ruby><rb>励精</rb><rt>れいせい</rt></ruby>&nbsp;diligence</span></span>で、――と<span class="vocab">のべつに<span class="vocabdef">のべつに&nbsp;ceaselessly</span></span><span class="vocab">弁じた<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>弁</rb><rt>べん</rt></ruby>じた&nbsp;spoke</span></span>のは<span class="vocab">愛嬌<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>愛嬌</rb><rt>あいきょう</rt></ruby>&nbsp;personal charm; engaging manner</span></span>のある<span class="vocab">お爺さん<span class="vocabdef">お<ruby><rb>爺</rb><rt>じい</rt></ruby>さん&nbsp;older gentleman</span></span>だ。<span class="vocab">画学<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>画学</rb><rt>ががく</rt></ruby>&nbsp;drawing; art</span></span>の教師は<span class="vocab">全く<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>全</rb><rt>まった</rt></ruby>く&nbsp;completely</span></span><span class="vocab">芸人<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>芸人</rb><rt>げいにん</rt></ruby>&nbsp;artist; performer</span></span><span class="vocab">風<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>風</rb><rt>ふう</rt></ruby>&nbsp;style; type</span></span>だ。<span class="vocab">べらべらした<span class="vocabdef">べらべらした&nbsp;thin; flimsy</span></span><span class="vocab">透綾<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>透綾</rb><rt>すきや</rt></ruby>&nbsp;thin silk material</span></span>の<span class="vocab">羽織<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>羽織</rb><rt>はおり</rt></ruby>&nbsp;haori (Japanese half-coat)</span></span>を着て、<span class="vocab">扇子<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>扇子</rb><rt>せんす</rt></ruby>&nbsp;(folding) fan</span></span>を<span class="vocab">ぱちつかせて<span class="vocabdef">ぱちつかせて&nbsp;wielding</span></span>、<span class="vocab">お国<span class="vocabdef">お<ruby><rb>国</rb><rt>くに</rt></ruby>&nbsp;home (country); native region</span></span>はどちらでげす、え？　<span class="vocab">東京<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>東京</rb><rt>とうきょう</rt></ruby>&nbsp;Tōkyō</span></span>？　そりゃ<span class="vocab">嬉しい<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>嬉</rb><rt>うれ</rt></ruby>しい&nbsp;glad</span></span>、<span class="vocab">お仲間<span class="vocabdef">お<ruby><rb>仲間</rb><rt>なかま</rt></ruby>&nbsp;comrade</span></span>が<span class="vocab">出来て<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>出来</rb><rt>でき</rt></ruby>て&nbsp;form; be established</span></span>……<span class="vocab">私<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>私</rb><rt>わたし</rt></ruby>&nbsp;I</span></span>もこれで<span class="vocab">江戸っ子<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>江戸</rb><rt>えど</rt></ruby>っ<ruby><rb>子</rb><rt>こ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;native of Tōkyō (Edo = pre-Meiji name for Tōkyō)</span></span>ですと云った。こんなのが江戸っ子なら江戸には<span class="vocab">生れたくない<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>生</rb><rt>うま</rt></ruby>れたくない&nbsp;do not want to have been born (there)</span></span>もんだと<span class="vocab">心中に<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>心中</rb><rt>しんちゅう</rt></ruby>に&nbsp;at heart; innermost (thoughts)</span></span><span class="vocab">考えた<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>考</rb><rt>かんが</rt></ruby>えた&nbsp;thought; considered</span></span>。そのほか<span class="vocab">一人一人<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>一人一人</rb><rt>ひとりびとり</rt></ruby>&nbsp;each person; one by one</span></span>についてこんな事を<span class="vocab">書けば<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>書</rb><rt>か</rt></ruby>けば&nbsp;(if I) write</span></span>いくらでもある。しかし<span class="vocab">際限がない<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>際限</rb><rt>さいげん</rt></ruby>がない&nbsp;would go on forever</span></span>からやめる。</p>

