<p><span class="vocab">手紙<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>手紙</rb><rt>てがみ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;letter</span></span>をかいてしまったら、いい<span class="vocab">心持ち<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>心持</rb><rt>こころも</rt></ruby>ち&nbsp;feeling</span></span>になって<span class="vocab">眠気<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>眠気</rb><rt>ねむけ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;drowsiness</span></span>がさしたから、<span class="vocab">最前<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>最前</rb><rt>さいぜん</rt></ruby>&nbsp;a short time earlier</span></span>のように<span class="vocab">座敷<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>座敷</rb><rt>ざしき</rt></ruby>&nbsp;room</span></span>の<span class="vocab">真中<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>真中</rb><rt>まんなか</rt></ruby>&nbsp;right in the middle</span></span>へのびのびと<span class="vocab">大の字に<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>大</rb><rt>だい</rt></ruby>の<ruby><rb>字</rb><rt>じ</rt></ruby>に&nbsp;like the character 大</span></span><span class="vocab">寝た<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>寝</rb><rt>ね</rt></ruby>た&nbsp;slept</span></span>。<span class="vocab">今度<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>今度</rb><rt>こんど</rt></ruby>&nbsp;this time</span></span>は<span class="vocab">夢<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>夢</rb><rt>ゆめ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;dream</span></span>も<span class="vocab">何も<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>何</rb><rt>なに</rt></ruby>も&nbsp;(not) anything</span></span><span class="vocab">見ない<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>見</rb><rt>み</rt></ruby>ない&nbsp;not see</span></span>でぐっすり寝た。この<span class="vocab">部屋<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>部屋</rb><rt>へや</rt></ruby>&nbsp;room</span></span>かいと<span class="vocab">大きな<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>大</rb><rt>おお</rt></ruby>きな&nbsp;large; loud</span></span><span class="vocab">声<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>声</rb><rt>こえ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;voice</span></span>がするので<span class="vocab">目<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>目</rb><rt>め</rt></ruby>&nbsp;eyes</span></span>が<span class="vocab">覚めたら<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>覚</rb><rt>さ</rt></ruby>めたら&nbsp;awakened</span></span>、<span class="vocab">山嵐<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>山嵐</rb><rt>やまあらし</rt></ruby>&nbsp;Yama Arashi (nickname for Hotta, the head mathematics teacher)</span></span>が<span class="vocab">はいって来た<span class="vocabdef">はいって<ruby><rb>来</rb><rt>き</rt></ruby>た&nbsp;entered</span></span>。最前は<span class="vocab">失敬<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>失敬</rb><rt>しっけい</rt></ruby>&nbsp;rudeness</span></span>、<span class="vocab">君<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>君</rb><rt>きみ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;you</span></span>の<span class="vocab">受持ち<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>受持</rb><rt>うけも</rt></ruby>ち&nbsp;one's responsibilities</span></span>は……と<span class="vocab">人<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>人</rb><rt>ひと</rt></ruby>&nbsp;a person</span></span>が<span class="vocab">起き上がる<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>起</rb><rt>お</rt></ruby>き<ruby><rb>上</rb><rt>あ</rt></ruby>がる&nbsp;wake up</span></span><span class="vocab">や否や<span class="vocabdef">や<ruby><rb>否</rb><rt>いな</rt></ruby>や&nbsp;as soon as</span></span><span class="vocab">談判<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>談判</rb><rt>だんぱん</rt></ruby>&nbsp;conference; conversation</span></span>を<span class="vocab">開かれた<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>開</rb><rt>ひら</rt></ruby>かれた&nbsp;began</span></span>ので<span class="vocab">大いに<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>大</rb><rt>おお</rt></ruby>いに&nbsp;considerably</span></span><span class="vocab">狼狽した<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>狼狽</rb><rt>ろうばい</rt></ruby>した&nbsp;panicked; felt confused</span></span>。受持ちを<span class="vocab">聞いて<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>聞</rb><rt>き</rt></ruby>いて&nbsp;listen to</span></span>みると<span class="vocab">別段<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>別段</rb><rt>べつだん</rt></ruby>&nbsp;particularly</span></span>むずかしい<span class="vocab">事<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>事</rb><rt>こと</rt></ruby>&nbsp;act; fact</span></span>もなさそうだから<span class="vocab">承知した<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>承知</rb><rt>しょうち</rt></ruby>した&nbsp;consented to; agreed to</span></span>。このくらいの事なら、<span class="vocab">明後日<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>明後日</rb><rt>あさって</rt></ruby>&nbsp;day after tomorrow</span></span>は<span class="vocab">愚<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>愚</rb><rt>おろか</rt></ruby>&nbsp;foolishness</span></span>、<span class="vocab">明日<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>明日</rb><rt>あした</rt></ruby>&nbsp;tomorrow</span></span>から<span class="vocab">始めろ<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>始</rb><rt>はじ</rt></ruby>めろ&nbsp;begin (imperative form)</span></span>と<span class="vocab">云ったって<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>云</rb><rt>い</rt></ruby>ったって&nbsp;(even if he) said</span></span><span class="vocab">驚ろかない<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>驚</rb><rt>おど</rt></ruby>ろかない&nbsp;(I) would not be surprised</span></span>。<span class="vocab">授業上の<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>授業上</rb><rt>じゅぎょうじょう</rt></ruby>の&nbsp;concerning teaching</span></span><span class="vocab">打ち合せ<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>打</rb><rt>う</rt></ruby>ち<ruby><rb>合</rb><rt>あわ</rt></ruby>せ&nbsp;discussion</span></span>が<span class="vocab">済んだら<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>済</rb><rt>す</rt></ruby>んだら&nbsp;(when it was) ended</span></span>、君はいつまでこんな<span class="vocab">宿屋<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>宿屋</rb><rt>やどや</rt></ruby>&nbsp;inn</span></span>に<span class="vocab">居る<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>居</rb><rt>い</rt></ruby>る&nbsp;be; stay</span></span>つもりでもあるまい、<span class="vocab">僕<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>僕</rb><rt>ぼく</rt></ruby>&nbsp;I</span></span>がいい<span class="vocab">下宿<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>下宿</rb><rt>げしゅく</rt></ruby>&nbsp;lodgings</span></span>を<span class="vocab">周旋して<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>周旋</rb><rt>しゅうせん</rt></ruby>して&nbsp;arrange; intercede (on behalf of someone)</span></span>やるから<span class="vocab">移りたまえ<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>移</rb><rt>うつ</rt></ruby>りたまえ&nbsp;please relocate</span></span>。<span class="vocab">外<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>外</rb><rt>ほか</rt></ruby>&nbsp;other</span></span>のものでは承知しないが僕が<span class="vocab">話せば<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>話</rb><rt>はな</rt></ruby>せば&nbsp;(provided I) talk (to them)</span></span>すぐ<span class="vocab">出来る<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>出来</rb><rt>でき</rt></ruby>る&nbsp;can be done</span></span>。<span class="vocab">早い<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>早</rb><rt>はや</rt></ruby>い&nbsp;soon</span></span><span class="vocab">方<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>方</rb><rt>ほう</rt></ruby>&nbsp;alternative</span></span>がいいから、<span class="vocab">今日<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>今日</rb><rt>きょう</rt></ruby>&nbsp;today</span></span>見て、あす移って、あさってから<span class="vocab">学校<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>学校</rb><rt>がっこう</rt></ruby>&nbsp;school</span></span>へ<span class="vocab">行けば<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>行</rb><rt>い</rt></ruby>けば&nbsp;go (provisional form)</span></span><span class="vocab">極りがいい<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>極</rb><rt>きま</rt></ruby>りがいい&nbsp;will be settled nicely</span></span>と<span class="vocab">一人で<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>一人</rb><rt>ひとり</rt></ruby>で&nbsp;by oneself; on one's own</span></span><span class="vocab">呑み込んで<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>呑</rb><rt>の</rt></ruby>み<ruby><rb>込</rb><rt>こ</rt></ruby>んで&nbsp;figured out</span></span>いる。なるほど<span class="vocab">十五畳敷<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>十五畳敷</rb><rt>じゅうごじょうじき</rt></ruby>&nbsp;15-mat room</span></span>にいつまで居る<span class="vocab">訳<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>訳</rb><rt>わけ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;reason; cause</span></span>にも行くまい。<span class="vocab">月給<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>月給</rb><rt>げっきゅう</rt></ruby>&nbsp;salary</span></span>をみんな<span class="vocab">宿料<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>宿料</rb><rt>しゅくりょう</rt></ruby>&nbsp;room charges</span></span>に<span class="vocab">払って<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>払</rb><rt>はら</rt></ruby>って&nbsp;pay; spend</span></span>も<span class="vocab">追っつかない<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>追</rb><rt>お</rt></ruby>っつかない&nbsp;not keep up</span></span>かもしれぬ。<span class="vocab">五円<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>五円</rb><rt>ごえん</rt></ruby>&nbsp;five yen</span></span>の<span class="vocab">茶代<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>茶代</rb><rt>ちゃだい</rt></ruby>&nbsp;tip</span></span>を<span class="vocab">奮発して<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>奮発</rb><rt>ふんぱつ</rt></ruby>して&nbsp;splurge (on)</span></span>すぐ移るのはちと<span class="vocab">残念<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>残念</rb><rt>ざんねん</rt></ruby>&nbsp;a pity; too bad</span></span>だが、どうせ移る<span class="vocab">者なら<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>者</rb><rt>もの</rt></ruby>なら&nbsp;if one has to ...</span></span>、早く<span class="vocab">引き越して<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>引</rb><rt>ひ</rt></ruby>き<ruby><rb>越</rb><rt>こ</rt></ruby>して&nbsp;move; relocate</span></span><span class="vocab">落ち付く<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>落</rb><rt>お</rt></ruby>ち<ruby><rb>付</rb><rt>つ</rt></ruby>く&nbsp;settle in</span></span>方が<span class="vocab">便利<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>便利</rb><rt>べんり</rt></ruby>&nbsp;expediency</span></span>だから、そこのところはよろしく山嵐に<span class="vocab">頼む<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>頼</rb><rt>たの</rt></ruby>む&nbsp;request; look to (a person for help)</span></span>事にした。すると山嵐はともかくもいっしょに来てみろと云うから、行った。<span class="vocab">町はずれ<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>町</rb><rt>まち</rt></ruby>はずれ&nbsp;the edge of town</span></span>の<span class="vocab">岡<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>岡</rb><rt>おか</rt></ruby>&nbsp;hill</span></span>の<span class="vocab">中腹<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>中腹</rb><rt>ちゅうふく</rt></ruby>&nbsp;halfway (up a  hill)</span></span>にある<span class="vocab">家<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>家</rb><rt>いえ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;house</span></span>で<span class="vocab">至極<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>至極</rb><rt>しごく</rt></ruby>&nbsp;extremely</span></span><span class="vocab">閑静<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>閑静</rb><rt>かんせい</rt></ruby>&nbsp;quiet; tranquil</span></span>だ。<span class="vocab">主人<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>主人</rb><rt>しゅじん</rt></ruby>&nbsp;the husband</span></span>は<span class="vocab">骨董<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>骨董</rb><rt>こっとう</rt></ruby>&nbsp;curios; antiques</span></span>を<span class="vocab">売買する<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>売買</rb><rt>ばいばい</rt></ruby>する&nbsp;trade; buy and sell; deal in</span></span><span class="vocab">いか銀<span class="vocabdef">いか<ruby><rb>銀</rb><rt>ぎん</rt></ruby>&nbsp;Ikagin (name)</span></span>と云う<span class="vocab">男<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>男</rb><rt>おとこ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;man</span></span>で、<span class="vocab">女房<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>女房</rb><rt>にょうぼう</rt></ruby>&nbsp;the wife</span></span>は<span class="vocab">亭主<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>亭主</rb><rt>ていしゅ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;husband</span></span>よりも<span class="vocab">四つ<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>四</rb><rt>よっ</rt></ruby>つ&nbsp;four (years)</span></span>ばかり<span class="vocab">年嵩<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>年嵩</rb><rt>としかさ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;elder</span></span>の<span class="vocab">女<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>女</rb><rt>おんな</rt></ruby>&nbsp;woman</span></span>だ。<span class="vocab">中学校<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>中学校</rb><rt>ちゅうがっこう</rt></ruby>&nbsp;middle school</span></span>に居た<span class="vocab">時<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>時</rb><rt>とき</rt></ruby>&nbsp;time; period</span></span>ウィッチと云う<span class="vocab">言葉<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>言葉</rb><rt>ことば</rt></ruby>&nbsp;word</span></span>を<span class="vocab">習った<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>習</rb><rt>なら</rt></ruby>った&nbsp;learned</span></span>事があるがこの女房はまさにウィッチに<span class="vocab">似ている<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>似</rb><rt>に</rt></ruby>ている&nbsp;looked like; resembled</span></span>。ウィッチだって人の女房だから<span class="vocab">構わない<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>構</rb><rt>かま</rt></ruby>わない&nbsp;doesn't matter (to me)</span></span>。とうとう<span class="vocab">明日<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>明日</rb><rt>あした</rt></ruby>&nbsp;tomorrow; the next day</span></span>から引き移る事にした。<span class="vocab">帰り<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>帰</rb><rt>かえ</rt></ruby>り&nbsp;return</span></span>に山嵐は<span class="vocab">通町<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>通町</rb><rt>とおりちょう</rt></ruby>&nbsp;Tōrichō (place name - old)</span></span>で<span class="vocab">氷水<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>氷水</rb><rt>こおりみず</rt></ruby>&nbsp;ice water</span></span>を<span class="vocab">一杯<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>一杯</rb><rt>いっぱい</rt></ruby>&nbsp;one cup</span></span><span class="vocab">奢った<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>奢</rb><rt>おご</rt></ruby>った&nbsp;treated (someone to something)</span></span>。学校で<span class="vocab">逢った<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>逢</rb><rt>あ</rt></ruby>った&nbsp;met</span></span>時はやに<span class="vocab">横風な<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>横風</rb><rt>おうふう</rt></ruby>な&nbsp;arrogant</span></span>失敬な<span class="vocab">奴<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>奴</rb><rt>やつ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;fellow</span></span>だと<span class="vocab">思った<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>思</rb><rt>おも</rt></ruby>った&nbsp;thought</span></span>が、こんなにいろいろ<span class="vocab">世話<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>世話</rb><rt>せわ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;help; assistance</span></span>をしてくれるところを見ると、わるい男でもなさそうだ。ただおれと<span class="vocab">同じ<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>同</rb><rt>おの</rt></ruby>じ&nbsp;same</span></span>ように<span class="vocab">せっかち<span class="vocabdef">せっかち&nbsp;hasty; quick-tempered</span></span>で<span class="vocab">肝癪持<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>肝癪持</rb><rt>かんしゃくもち</rt></ruby>&nbsp;hot-headed</span></span>らしい。あとで聞いたらこの男が<span class="vocab">一番<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>一番</rb><rt>いちばん</rt></ruby>&nbsp;most</span></span><span class="vocab">生徒<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>生徒</rb><rt>せいと</rt></ruby>&nbsp;students</span></span>に<span class="vocab">人望<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>人望</rb><rt>じんぼう</rt></ruby>&nbsp;popularity; favorable reputation</span></span>があるのだそうだ。</p>
